WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.159
And we studied on Wednesday evenings earlier this year that very thought of the names of

00:00:05.159 --> 00:00:07.119
God and what a blessing.

00:00:07.119 --> 00:00:11.600
And thankful for the opportunity to be able to sing some songs together this evening.

00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:16.600
Luke chapter number five in your Bible, Luke chapter number five, and looking forward to

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:19.079
what God has in store for us this evening.

00:00:19.079 --> 00:00:25.340
It's a familiar passage of scripture and something that I'm sure many of us have heard.

00:00:25.340 --> 00:00:29.979
