00:01:48.739 --> 00:01:55.739
And Simon answering said unto him, Master, we have toiled all the night and have taken

00:01:55.739 --> 00:01:56.739
nothing.

00:01:56.739 --> 00:02:02.739
Nevertheless, at thy word, I will let down the net.

00:02:02.739 --> 00:02:07.860
When they had this done, they enclosed a great multitude of fishes and their net break.

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:12.179
And they beckoned unto their partners, which were in the other ship, that they should come

00:02:12.179 --> 00:02:13.940
