00:02:18.059 --> 00:02:19.059
Can you imagine?

00:02:19.059 --> 00:02:21.500
I mean, this is absolutely amazing.

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:26.059
I can't imagine Peter and these others experiencing this firsthand.

00:02:26.059 --> 00:02:31.220
And it says in verse number eight, when Simon Peter saw it, he fell down at Jesus's knees

00:02:31.220 --> 00:02:35.500
