00:02:47.380 --> 00:02:53.860
And Jesus said unto Simon, fear not, from henceforth thou shalt catch men.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:59.039
When they had brought their ships to land, they forsook all and followed him.

00:02:59.039 --> 00:03:04.139
This evening from verse number seven, the Bible says they beckoned unto their partners,

00:03:04.139 --> 00:03:07.179
which were in the other ship, that they should come and help them.

00:03:07.179 --> 00:03:11.500
And I've simply titled the message tonight, Come and Help.

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:15.320
Notice with me as we study through this portion of scripture and find the immediate context

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:17.639
and what's taking place with this miracle.

00:03:17.639 --> 00:03:20.199
