00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:22.960
Notice with me, first of all, the master's command.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:27.839
By the way, I'm thankful that God has given to us his word and he's provided us with instruction.

00:03:27.839 --> 00:03:35.119
