00:46:26.359 --> 00:46:27.359
Some plant, some water.

00:46:27.359 --> 00:46:30.239
God, You're the one that gives the increase.

00:46:30.239 --> 00:46:31.879
And we want to be faithful.

00:46:31.879 --> 00:46:40.439
God, we want to, as You entrust us with guests, and visitors, and new move-ins, we want to

00:46:40.439 --> 00:46:44.679
be faithful to minister to them spiritually.

00:46:44.679 --> 00:46:47.879
And God, I pray that You'd help us.

00:46:47.879 --> 00:46:49.479
We can't do it on our own power.

00:46:49.479 --> 00:46:51.559
We need You.

00:46:51.559 --> 00:46:53.079
We need each other.

00:46:53.079 --> 00:46:57.479
As our folks go to their respective homes and workplaces, Lord, I pray that You'd help

00:46:57.479 --> 00:47:02.479
them to understand the sphere of influence that You've given them, the opportunities

00:47:02.479 --> 00:47:04.639
that You've set before them.

00:47:04.639 --> 00:47:12.919
I pray, God, that You'd use us to be a light in this region, Lord, that we'd see many come

00:47:12.919 --> 00:47:14.559
to Christ.

00:47:14.559 --> 00:47:17.279
I pray in this time of invitation that You'd have Your will in way.

00:47:17.279 --> 00:47:20.599
I pray that You'd move in hearts as only You can.

00:47:20.599 --> 00:47:23.559
Lord, help us to be doers of the Word and not hearers only.

00:47:23.559 --> 00:47:25.039
Well, thank You for what You'll do.

00:47:25.039 --> 00:47:26.279
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:47:26.439 --> 00:47:27.439
Would you stand with me?

00:47:27.439 --> 00:47:28.439
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:47:28.439 --> 00:47:30.839
Kimberly's going to play quietly on the piano.

00:47:30.839 --> 00:47:32.719
Maybe tonight you want to come to this old-fashioned altar.

00:47:32.719 --> 00:47:36.079
Maybe you want to thank God for the opportunity to be engaged in the work.

00:47:36.079 --> 00:47:38.079
Maybe you want to make a commitment to the Lord.

00:47:38.079 --> 00:47:43.759
Maybe you want to renew a commitment of being that witness that God has called you to be

00:47:43.759 --> 00:47:45.639
as Kimberly plays, the altar is open.

